 and\nthe position of individual photons at the surface of the detector to\n$\\le$100~ps and a few mm, respectively, we have measured a spatial resolution\nof $\\sim$ 15~mm for each MCP-PMT track segment, and, from linear fits over the\nentire track length of $\\sim40$~cm, an angular resolution on the track\ndirection of $\\sim60$~mrad.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Oct 2015 15:59:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
